1
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:34,860
[Strange Tales of Tang Dynasty III:
To Chang'an]

2
00:01:35,770 --> 00:01:38,030
[Episode 36]

3
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:43,229
Rest assured, Grand General.

4
00:01:43,229 --> 00:01:44,229
I will catch

5
00:01:44,229 --> 00:01:45,310
the spies from Yenisei Kirghiz
as soon as possible

6
00:01:45,310 --> 00:01:46,710
to keep the capital safe.

7
00:01:47,070 --> 00:01:48,509
His Majesty is attending
the Polo Tournament

8
00:01:48,509 --> 00:01:49,840
in person.

9
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,600
There must be no mishaps.

10
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:53,650
Understood.

11
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:56,509
Please.

12
00:01:57,310 --> 00:01:58,039
Official Lu.

13
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,000
Grand General.

14
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,600
What is it?

15
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,070
Why don't you see Grand General off first?

16
00:02:06,070 --> 00:02:07,040
Xue Huan, right?

17
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:09,060
Are you hiding something from me?

18
00:02:09,590 --> 00:02:10,449
Speak plainly.

19
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:12,680
Chancellor Cui has suddenly visited,

20
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,840
walking here as we speak.

21
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:14,970
I couldn't stop him.

22
00:02:19,590 --> 00:02:20,520
Chancellor Cui.

23
00:02:23,190 --> 00:02:26,000
Alright, no need to see me out then.

24
00:02:31,150 --> 00:02:32,150
Her Majesty is looking for you.

25
00:02:32,150 --> 00:02:32,910
Come with me.

26
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,240
Your Highness, what are your orders?

27
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:52,960
Ji,

28
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,200
come quickly.

29
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:55,060
Have a seat.

30
00:03:01,590 --> 00:03:02,450
Ji,

31
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,910
you haven't visited me for days.

32
00:03:06,190 --> 00:03:07,590
You've been solving mysterious cases
one after another,

33
00:03:07,590 --> 00:03:08,800
achieving remarkable merits,

34
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,130
so you must be very busy.

35
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:11,680
But

36
00:03:12,190 --> 00:03:13,910
I miss you, my son.

37
00:03:14,310 --> 00:03:16,230
How has Your Highness been feeling lately?

38
00:03:16,230 --> 00:03:18,440
My health is fine,

39
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,430
but

40
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:23,000
my mood is not.

41
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:24,810
What troubles you?

42
00:03:25,630 --> 00:03:26,560
I've been worried about

43
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,420
the prosperity of our Tang Empire

44
00:03:28,470 --> 00:03:29,960
every day.

45
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:34,470
Are you planning to say that

46
00:03:34,710 --> 00:03:36,240
with His Majesty in charge,

47
00:03:36,470 --> 00:03:37,870
I shouldn't worry?

48
00:03:40,340 --> 00:03:41,520
I wouldn't dare think that.

49
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:44,350
I am the Grand Princess
of the Tang Empire.

50
00:03:45,140 --> 00:03:47,650
Tang Empire's affairs are my affairs.

51
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:51,520
Take the foreign nation,
Yenisei Kirghiz, for example.

52
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,120
They have been eyeing our borders

53
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:55,280
with covetous intent.

54
00:03:55,590 --> 00:03:56,800
My heart

55
00:03:57,850 --> 00:03:59,370
will never be at peace

56
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,090
until they are eliminated.

57
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,560
During Empress Wu Zetian's reign,

58
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,800
at the Battle of Wushan,

59
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,400
our army suffered a terrible defeat

60
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,860
which boosted the foreign nation's morale.

61
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:10,780
Lu Lingfeng,

62
00:04:10,810 --> 00:04:11,940
let me tell you.

63
00:04:12,150 --> 00:04:14,910
Yenisei Kirghiz excels at espionage.

64
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:17,089
It's said that in Chang'an,

65
00:04:17,510 --> 00:04:19,800
they've planted formidable spies

66
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:22,370
who are now stirring

67
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,340
with malicious intent.

68
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,860
Yenisei Kirghiz is also
skilled at sowing discord.

69
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,120
If you captured any spies,

70
00:04:30,190 --> 00:04:31,440
just kill them.

71
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,360
No need for interrogation.

72
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,950
Whatever they confess

73
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:37,880
will just be pre-fabricated lies
meant to divide us.

74
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:39,830
Do you understand

75
00:04:40,270 --> 00:04:41,470
what I'm telling you?

76
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:47,890
Her Highness really said that?

77
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:51,230
For once,

78
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:52,000
I fail to grasp

79
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,600
any of her hidden messages.

80
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,940
Then, let's do it this way.

81
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:58,420
Once a Yenisei Kirghiz spy is caught,

82
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,420
if they confess

83
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:01,120
to having connections
with the Princess's Mansion,

84
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,580
we kill them immediately.

85
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,750
Su Wuming, you...

86
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:08,630
The Princess mentioning this in advance

87
00:05:08,630 --> 00:05:09,560
proves that her household

88
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:12,000
indeed has connections
with the Yenisei Kirghiz.

89
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:15,120
But if Yenisei Kirghiz
intends to cause chaos in our empire,

90
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,560
Her Highness would never do anything

91
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:18,270
to help them.

92
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:20,880
That's what Her Highness means.

93
00:05:21,270 --> 00:05:22,330
Do you understand?

94
00:05:23,510 --> 00:05:24,230
Well...

95
00:05:24,430 --> 00:05:25,430
Are you currently

96
00:05:25,430 --> 00:05:27,630
investigating Yenisei Kirghiz spies?

97
00:05:28,070 --> 00:05:28,950
How did you know?

98
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:30,550
Doesn't it all fit together?

99
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,110
Go ahead with your investigation

100
00:05:32,110 --> 00:05:33,360
without hesitation.

101
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:36,800
I think I understand now.

102
00:05:37,310 --> 00:05:39,240
The Princess's Mansion must have
also received

103
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:41,240
intel about
the Yenisei Kirghiz spies,

104
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:43,240
but cannot speak about it directly.

105
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:44,070
Exactly.

106
00:05:45,310 --> 00:05:46,330
Let me tell you.

107
00:05:47,190 --> 00:05:49,490
Whether it's His Majesty, Her Highness

108
00:05:49,630 --> 00:05:51,630
or even the Retired Emperor,

109
00:05:51,870 --> 00:05:54,560
they all have dedicated people
managing intel.

110
00:05:54,670 --> 00:05:57,270
Chang'an is the most crucial place
of the Tang Empire.

111
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:58,510
The capital is kept safe

112
00:05:58,510 --> 00:05:59,830
by brave soldiers

113
00:05:59,870 --> 00:06:00,920
and united citizens.

114
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:03,390
But we also need to gather intel
and anticipate threats

115
00:06:03,390 --> 00:06:04,560
to be truly secured.

116
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:10,110
Have you heard of
the Ghost Market Intel Stall?

117
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,400
More than just heard of it.

118
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:16,720
Back then, Master Di and I

119
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,500
even went there in disguise.

120
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,070
Your mentor went there too?

121
00:06:20,070 --> 00:06:20,720
Yes.

122
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:23,390
But the one from back then was destroyed.

123
00:06:23,390 --> 00:06:25,790
The current Intel Stall must be

124
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,170
rebuilt since then.

125
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:30,480
If I didn't have

126
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:31,430
cases to investigate,

127
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:33,040
I would really like to go with you

128
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,500
and revisit the old place.

129
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,090
So you're saying

130
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:36,870
you're unwilling

131
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:37,800
to go with me?

132
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,040
My dear Official Lu.

133
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:41,870
I am no longer

134
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:43,470
your Chief of Secret Agents.

135
00:06:43,630 --> 00:06:44,920
I am now

136
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,120
the Wannian County Sheriff.

137
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:46,920
I have

138
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:48,500
a lot on my plate too.

139
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:53,070
But I can't refuse

140
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,250
to help you, either.

141
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:54,890
Here's what I'll do.

142
00:06:54,890 --> 00:06:56,430
I'll give you

143
00:06:56,510 --> 00:06:57,570
an important lead.

144
00:06:58,190 --> 00:06:59,740
When the Yenisei Kirghiz come to Chang'an,

145
00:06:59,740 --> 00:07:03,160
they prefer staying at the Bafang Inn.

146
00:07:07,220 --> 00:07:10,690
[Liuhe Sushan Shop]

147
00:07:11,510 --> 00:07:14,560
These Yenisei Kirghiz
look just like our Tang people

148
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,390
with no noticeable differences.

149
00:07:16,390 --> 00:07:18,330
When they disguise themselves

150
00:07:18,390 --> 00:07:20,220
and wear our Tang clothing,

151
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:23,390
how can we identify them as spies?

152
00:07:25,430 --> 00:07:26,830
That's precisely why

153
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:28,390
I'm here

154
00:07:28,950 --> 00:07:30,860
to ask for your help, Fei.

155
00:07:31,070 --> 00:07:31,950
Ask for my help?

156
00:07:34,870 --> 00:07:36,510
I knew it.

157
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,659
The Chicken Master of Tang

158
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:41,290
is still quite useful after all.

159
00:07:42,310 --> 00:07:43,790
Catching a few spies

160
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:45,530
will be a piece of cake.

161
00:07:46,350 --> 00:07:47,820
Tell me, what's the plan?

162
00:07:48,180 --> 00:07:49,480
[Bafang Inn]

163
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,720
Fragrance pouches.

164
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,400
Fragrance pouches, anyone?

165
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:56,790
[Bafang Inn]

166
00:07:56,790 --> 00:07:58,430
Tofu.

167
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:00,470
Bafang Inn.

168
00:08:00,730 --> 00:08:02,530
That's right. This is the place.

169
00:08:21,980 --> 00:08:23,710
[Sixi Wonton] [Ten-year-old Shop]

170
00:08:24,990 --> 00:08:26,390
What smells so delicious?

171
00:08:26,390 --> 00:08:27,920
That'd be the Sixi Wontons.

172
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:29,630
Four different fillings in each bowl.

173
00:08:29,630 --> 00:08:30,710
Free soup refills.

174
00:08:30,950 --> 00:08:31,610
Want a bowl?

175
00:08:32,650 --> 00:08:33,850
I'll have one.

176
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,220
It smells amazing.

177
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:41,000
You must be the owner here.

178
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:41,600
Yes.

179
00:08:41,630 --> 00:08:42,630
What's your name?

180
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:42,940
Lady Chong the Thirty-Sixth.

181
00:08:42,940 --> 00:08:44,720
[Owner of Bafang Inn,
Lady Chong the Thirty-Sixth]

182
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,520
Nice name.

183
00:08:45,970 --> 00:08:47,170
I remember this place

184
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:49,950
used to be just an inn.

185
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:52,460
How come you're selling wontons now?

186
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,480
The inn business isn't doing well.

187
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,750
I had to start selling wontons too

188
00:08:55,750 --> 00:08:57,080
to afford the rent.

189
00:08:58,670 --> 00:09:00,340
I have an idea.

190
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:03,040
It could help you share some of the rent.

191
00:09:04,690 --> 00:09:07,230
Rent that empty space to me.

192
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:12,290
What do you want it for?

193
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:15,100
I want to open a branch of my Sushan Shop.

194
00:09:15,550 --> 00:09:16,360
Sushan?

195
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:18,870
I've heard of it.

196
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:19,910
It's just shaved ice, isn't it?

197
00:09:19,910 --> 00:09:20,440
Thats...

198
00:09:20,620 --> 00:09:22,170
That's not very nice of you.

199
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,540
I'm not renting it.

200
00:09:25,150 --> 00:09:26,970
You can't say no.

201
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:30,840
Because we're destined to work together.

202
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,220
What destiny?

203
00:09:32,220 --> 00:09:33,190
Look.

204
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:35,720
Your inn is called the Bafang Inn,

205
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,240
right?

206
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:38,550
These wontons are called Sixi Wonton,

207
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:39,200
right?

208
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:41,060
And my Sushan Shop

209
00:09:41,270 --> 00:09:42,990
is called Liuhe Sushan Shop.

210
00:09:43,270 --> 00:09:45,020
Isn't that destiny?

211
00:09:45,150 --> 00:09:46,240
It's just a coincidence.

212
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,840
Stop trying to get friendly.

213
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:53,270
You said just now

214
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:56,250
that you're Lady Chong the Thirty-Sixth.

215
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,910
Six times six is thirty-six!

216
00:09:59,750 --> 00:10:02,320
This means my Liuhe Sushan Shop

217
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:04,030
was always meant to include you,

218
00:10:04,030 --> 00:10:06,100
Lady Chong the Thirty-Sixth.

219
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,030
It's your destiny!

220
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:10,280
If you flatly refuse,

221
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,600
it might bring you bad luck.

222
00:10:14,070 --> 00:10:15,500
I'm not opening this branch

223
00:10:15,500 --> 00:10:17,420
just to make money.

224
00:10:18,060 --> 00:10:20,720
I mainly want to promote sushan.

225
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:23,280
How about this? After the branch opens,

226
00:10:23,670 --> 00:10:25,150
anyone who eats your wontons

227
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:26,930
can buy my sushan at 40% off.

228
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,130
On top of that,

229
00:10:28,130 --> 00:10:29,550
those staying at your inn

230
00:10:30,030 --> 00:10:32,410
will each get a serving of sushan

231
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:33,630
for free.

232
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:34,810
How about it?

233
00:10:37,390 --> 00:10:38,000
You...

234
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:40,080
Are you serious?

235
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,330
Of course.

236
00:10:41,750 --> 00:10:43,270
That would cause you to lose money.

237
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:44,140
What's in it for you?

238
00:10:44,140 --> 00:10:45,630
Well, I'm here...

239
00:10:46,690 --> 00:10:48,380
For your beauty, of course.

240
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:51,310
Aren't you too old

241
00:10:51,390 --> 00:10:52,670
to take a fancy to me?

242
00:10:53,630 --> 00:10:55,910
Everyone has a love for beauty.

243
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,700
It has nothing to do with age.

244
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,300
I'm a gentleman.

245
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:01,380
I may admire you,

246
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:04,540
but I would never harass you.

247
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:07,150
You're certainly not off-putting.

248
00:11:07,150 --> 00:11:08,210
Then it's settled.

249
00:11:09,670 --> 00:11:12,150
Yang Ji!

250
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,220
Coming!

251
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:19,890
Pay your respects to the innkeeper.

252
00:11:19,890 --> 00:11:21,220
Greetings, Innkeeper.

253
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:24,350
He's our Sushan Shop's assistant.

254
00:11:24,550 --> 00:11:25,970
After the branch opens,

255
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:28,150
he'll be stationed here permanently.

256
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:29,440
If you need any heavy lifting done

257
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:31,310
at the wonton shop

258
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:32,760
or the inn,

259
00:11:32,920 --> 00:11:34,380
just call for him anytime.

260
00:11:35,020 --> 00:11:36,750
Yes, I have plenty of strength.

261
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:37,870
If you need any help,

262
00:11:37,870 --> 00:11:39,730
please don't hesitate to tell me.

263
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,440
Greetings, General.

264
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:07,550
Oh, it's you, Li Zhuang.

265
00:12:07,670 --> 00:12:08,270
I already knew

266
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:09,480
you left the Imperial Guard.

267
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,320
But I didn't expect that

268
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,150
you were collecting intel

269
00:12:11,150 --> 00:12:12,340
for the Grand General.

270
00:12:12,340 --> 00:12:13,200
[Court of State Ceremonials, Li Zhuang]

271
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,130
My duty needed me

272
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:16,330
to keep my special identity a secret,

273
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,530
so I couldn't inform you, General.

274
00:12:19,390 --> 00:12:20,190
I understand.

275
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:20,980
Have a seat.

276
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,840
Where do you normally work?

277
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:28,770
At the Court of State Ceremonials.

278
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:32,000
That would indeed help

279
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,340
with gathering intel.

280
00:12:33,390 --> 00:12:35,050
But I heard this intel

281
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,630
came from the Ghost Market.

282
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:38,270
Gathering intel
through foreign delegations

283
00:12:38,270 --> 00:12:39,640
is too difficult.

284
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:40,980
After all, many of them

285
00:12:40,980 --> 00:12:42,360
have the same role as I do.

286
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,600
They either keep their mouths shut

287
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,750
or spread false intel

288
00:12:44,750 --> 00:12:45,950
to create confusion.

289
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,330
I still have to do my job.

290
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:50,200
So I had to send my secret agents

291
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:51,360
to frequent the Intel Stall

292
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:52,490
at the Ghost Market.

293
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:53,130
And look,

294
00:12:53,180 --> 00:12:54,110
we obtained this

295
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:55,380
useful piece of intel.

296
00:12:55,670 --> 00:12:57,070
Who is this secret agent?

297
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,430
A man named Liu Xi.

298
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,600
How much did this intel cost?

299
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:01,980
100,000 coins.

300
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:04,750
Li Zhuang.

301
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:06,630
You're quite generous.

302
00:13:08,010 --> 00:13:10,000
Useful intel is expensive.

303
00:13:13,020 --> 00:13:14,150
I want to meet Liu Xi.

304
00:13:18,870 --> 00:13:19,840
How annoying.

305
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:26,440
You may go.

306
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,050
Liu Xi.

307
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:46,630
In you go.

308
00:13:52,030 --> 00:13:52,550
I...

309
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:58,120
Forgive my poor eyesight.

310
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:00,790
Could you be Official Lu?

311
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,120
You know me?

312
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,870
You're from the famous
Lu family of Fanyang,

313
00:14:06,870 --> 00:14:08,510
and your mother is the Grand Princess.

314
00:14:08,510 --> 00:14:10,510
So you come to places like this, too?

315
00:14:10,630 --> 00:14:11,560
What did you say?

316
00:14:11,670 --> 00:14:14,120
Did I say something wrong?

317
00:14:15,610 --> 00:14:18,270
[Secret agent, Liu Xi]

318
00:14:18,270 --> 00:14:19,510
Right, your relationship with the Princess

319
00:14:19,510 --> 00:14:20,720
hasn't been made public yet.

320
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:21,650
But don't forget

321
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:23,350
what I do for a living.

322
00:14:23,670 --> 00:14:24,870
As early as a year ago,

323
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:26,790
someone at the Ghost Market

324
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:29,480
was already selling intel
about your mysterious background.

325
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,880
It was worth 5,000 coins.

326
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:31,960
Cut the nonsense.

327
00:14:32,390 --> 00:14:34,150
About the intel
you sold to Li Zhuang,

328
00:14:34,150 --> 00:14:35,630
who at the Ghost Market Intel Stall

329
00:14:35,630 --> 00:14:36,720
did you get it from?

330
00:14:39,510 --> 00:14:41,350
Sun Zi.

331
00:14:41,630 --> 00:14:42,670
Who is Sun Zi?

332
00:14:42,790 --> 00:14:45,450
He's the tenant
of the Ghost Market Intel Stall.

333
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,150
That place is the most active

334
00:14:47,150 --> 00:14:48,950
intel market in all of Chang'an.

335
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,930
That naturally makes Sun Zi

336
00:14:51,020 --> 00:14:52,600
the biggest intel broker.

337
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:54,510
Is the intel true or false?

338
00:14:54,510 --> 00:14:56,390
It can't be false this time.

339
00:14:56,670 --> 00:14:58,080
After all, I spent so much money.

340
00:14:58,080 --> 00:15:00,320
You get what you pay for.

341
00:15:01,510 --> 00:15:03,640
If there's nothing else, then I'll...

342
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:07,410
How about this?

343
00:15:07,510 --> 00:15:09,870
Why don't you join me for some fun?

344
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:10,910
I heard that

345
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:13,030
two new foreign dancers joined yesterday.

346
00:15:13,030 --> 00:15:14,170
They're quite good.

347
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:15,240
My treat.

348
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:18,250
Take me to the Ghost Market.

349
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:19,910
I want to meet Sun Zi.

350
00:15:29,250 --> 00:15:33,550
[Intel Stall]

351
00:15:33,550 --> 00:15:34,790
So there really is an Intel Stall.

352
00:15:34,790 --> 00:15:35,510
Chang'an

353
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:37,120
truly has everything for sale.

354
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:39,580
Free, open, inclusive, and accommodating.

355
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:41,260
That's the charm of Chang'an.

356
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:47,210
[Luoyang Directions]

357
00:15:51,980 --> 00:15:53,040
It's just up ahead.

358
00:15:53,870 --> 00:15:54,800
Are you alright?

359
00:15:56,790 --> 00:15:59,060
I've twisted my ankle.

360
00:15:59,510 --> 00:16:02,090
Sun Zi should be in the backyard.

361
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:03,520
Please, after you.

362
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:33,680
Be careful, Huan.

363
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:41,790
I'll go after them.

364
00:16:41,790 --> 00:16:42,790
You catch Liu Xi.

365
00:16:43,030 --> 00:16:43,510
Yes.

366
00:17:15,069 --> 00:17:16,550
Yongzhou Judicial Official investigating.

367
00:17:16,550 --> 00:17:18,079
Confess who's behind this.

368
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:30,350
This price won't do.

369
00:17:30,350 --> 00:17:31,080
It's too low.

370
00:17:31,510 --> 00:17:32,110
Liu Xi!

371
00:17:32,510 --> 00:17:33,070
Stop!

372
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:42,720
Murder!

373
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:43,600
Murder?

374
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:44,510
Let's go!

375
00:17:50,900 --> 00:17:51,960
He's already dead.

376
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:53,250
I found out just now

377
00:17:53,250 --> 00:17:54,830
that Sun Zi,
the tenant of the Intel Stall,

378
00:17:54,830 --> 00:17:55,270
didn't even

379
00:17:55,270 --> 00:17:57,000
come to the Ghost Market today.

380
00:17:57,030 --> 00:17:58,220
He has a house in Chang'an.

381
00:17:58,220 --> 00:17:59,820
It's in the Fengyi District.

382
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:05,170
It's just ahead.

383
00:18:08,310 --> 00:18:08,960
This is it.

384
00:18:10,780 --> 00:18:12,040
[Sun Mansion]

385
00:18:12,040 --> 00:18:12,550
Wait.

386
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:15,680
Is Sun Zi at home?

387
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:19,550
Sun Zi.

388
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:21,640
Sun Zi.

389
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:29,650
Xue Huan,

390
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:31,380
catch that woman just now!

391
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:37,480
Sun Zi!

392
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:38,550
Sun Zi!

393
00:18:41,470 --> 00:18:43,230
Save me...

394
00:18:48,030 --> 00:18:48,680
Stop!

395
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:14,550
[Yongzhou Prefecture]

396
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:20,210
Alright, you can question him now.

397
00:19:20,510 --> 00:19:21,790
He won't die for now.

398
00:19:23,440 --> 00:19:26,500
Thank you for saving my life.

399
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:28,400
He still has gratitude.

400
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:30,320
He shouldn't be a bad person.

401
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:35,520
Lu Lingfeng,

402
00:19:35,750 --> 00:19:37,270
I helped you save someone

403
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:38,600
and now I'm starving.

404
00:19:39,070 --> 00:19:40,030
Can your Yongzhou Prefecture

405
00:19:40,030 --> 00:19:41,440
get me a chicken?

406
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:43,240
You know how it is.

407
00:19:43,310 --> 00:19:45,880
The Princess appointed me as
the Chicken Master of Tang.

408
00:19:45,880 --> 00:19:47,950
I can eat chicken wherever I go.

409
00:19:48,960 --> 00:19:50,030
It seems to be

410
00:19:50,110 --> 00:19:51,400
Yongzhou Prefecture's turn.

411
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:52,110
Fei.

412
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:54,880
This is a critical moment
in our investigation.

413
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:57,210
Look at Xue Huan, he's lecturing me again.

414
00:19:58,400 --> 00:19:59,070
Fine, fine.

415
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:00,270
I'll just

416
00:20:00,680 --> 00:20:02,560
go to Bafang Inn

417
00:20:02,720 --> 00:20:04,950
and have a bowl of Sixi Wonton.

418
00:20:05,110 --> 00:20:05,830
Thank you, Fei.

419
00:20:05,830 --> 00:20:06,350
Save it.

420
00:20:08,360 --> 00:20:11,120
[Fair & Square]

421
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:13,130
Miracle Doctor Fei?

422
00:20:14,800 --> 00:20:15,930
Miracle Doctor Fei!

423
00:20:16,060 --> 00:20:17,590
[Remonstrance] [Fair & Square]

424
00:20:17,590 --> 00:20:18,910
Xiong Qiannian!

425
00:20:19,090 --> 00:20:20,490
I've missed you dearly

426
00:20:20,590 --> 00:20:22,120
since we parted in Nanzhou.

427
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:24,370
I've missed you too.

428
00:20:24,680 --> 00:20:26,010
When I was in Nanzhou,

429
00:20:26,270 --> 00:20:26,920
especially

430
00:20:26,920 --> 00:20:28,790
during those days when I arrived early,

431
00:20:28,790 --> 00:20:30,040
your hospitality

432
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:31,970
was truly exceptional.

433
00:20:33,200 --> 00:20:35,200
See? Good deeds bring good rewards.

434
00:20:35,270 --> 00:20:36,270
You've come to Chang'an

435
00:20:36,270 --> 00:20:38,590
and become Yongzhou's Chief Administrator.

436
00:20:38,590 --> 00:20:40,640
It's all thanks to your blessing.

437
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:43,080
What brings you

438
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:45,140
to Yongzhou Prefecture?

439
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:48,720
Just helping Lu Lingfeng
with some small matters.

440
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:52,400
That means you're helping
the county office.

441
00:20:52,400 --> 00:20:54,860
I, Xiong, express my gratitude.

442
00:20:56,590 --> 00:20:58,190
Haven't eaten yet, have you?

443
00:20:58,830 --> 00:21:01,070
I still have a few free-range chickens

444
00:21:01,240 --> 00:21:02,440
from Nanzhou with me.

445
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:04,590
For Laoshaoxiangxie?

446
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:06,720
It just so happens that

447
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:08,790
I also bought some tender bamboo shoots.

448
00:21:08,790 --> 00:21:10,240
The bamboo shoots in Chang'an,

449
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:12,070
though not as good as those in Nanzhou,

450
00:21:12,070 --> 00:21:13,710
are still acceptable.

451
00:21:14,830 --> 00:21:17,050
Then let's make do with them.

452
00:21:17,200 --> 00:21:17,720
Sun Zi.

453
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:19,590
Although you're severely injured,

454
00:21:19,590 --> 00:21:21,200
the case cannot be delayed.

455
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:23,480
You must answer my questions truthfully.

456
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:25,210
Official Lu, you saved my life.

457
00:21:25,270 --> 00:21:26,530
You're my benefactor.

458
00:21:26,550 --> 00:21:27,270
Ask away.

459
00:21:27,750 --> 00:21:28,960
Do you know Liu Xi?

460
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:29,430
Yes.

461
00:21:29,430 --> 00:21:31,160
[Owner of the Intel Stall, Sun Zi]

462
00:21:31,160 --> 00:21:32,490
My misfortune this time

463
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:33,880
was brought by him.

464
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:35,930
What do you mean?

465
00:21:36,200 --> 00:21:38,120
Today, as soon as I left home,

466
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:40,020
I met a young woman.

467
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:41,830
She flirted with me.

468
00:21:42,640 --> 00:21:43,880
So I brought her home.

469
00:21:43,920 --> 00:21:44,380
Come in.

470
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:47,000
How lovely.

471
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:52,410
Beautiful lady, come here!

472
00:21:57,640 --> 00:21:59,200
Someone bought intel from you

473
00:21:59,200 --> 00:22:00,730
about the Yenisei Kirghiz.

474
00:22:01,000 --> 00:22:02,600
Where did you get your intel?

475
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:05,220
Who are you?

476
00:22:05,310 --> 00:22:06,970
Stop wasting time. Answer me!

477
00:22:08,090 --> 00:22:09,290
Even if you kill me,

478
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:10,790
I cannot tell you.

479
00:22:11,270 --> 00:22:12,730
It's the rule of our trade.

480
00:22:12,960 --> 00:22:14,240
I, Sun Zi, am the owner

481
00:22:14,350 --> 00:22:16,030
of the Ghost Market Intel Stall.

482
00:22:16,030 --> 00:22:16,890
I must not

483
00:22:17,190 --> 00:22:19,180
break the rules!

484
00:22:21,500 --> 00:22:23,630
You're quite a stickler for the rules.

485
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:26,200
What if I'm the one asking?

486
00:22:27,200 --> 00:22:28,530
I can't tell you either.

487
00:22:28,960 --> 00:22:30,960
But this concerns a mysterious case

488
00:22:31,070 --> 00:22:32,810
and the peace of Chang'an.

489
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:33,850
It even concerns

490
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,260
His Majesty's safety.

491
00:22:37,850 --> 00:22:40,240
I've been in this business
for over a decade.

492
00:22:40,240 --> 00:22:41,900
We have informants stationed

493
00:22:42,070 --> 00:22:43,200
in some foreign states,

494
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:45,400
especially those with tense relations

495
00:22:45,750 --> 00:22:46,950
with the Tang Empire,

496
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:48,830
like Yenisei Kirghiz.

497
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:51,110
This intel came from

498
00:22:53,350 --> 00:22:54,640
those informants,

499
00:22:54,720 --> 00:22:56,450
delivered by a carrier pigeon.

500
00:22:59,720 --> 00:23:00,850
That's no easy feat.

501
00:23:01,830 --> 00:23:03,960
Placing informants in foreign states

502
00:23:04,120 --> 00:23:05,780
must cost quite a bit of money.

503
00:23:06,310 --> 00:23:07,000
Of course.

504
00:23:07,720 --> 00:23:09,520
When did you receive this intel?

505
00:23:10,000 --> 00:23:10,930
Half a month ago.

506
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:12,640
And when was it sent

507
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:13,940
from Yenisei Kirghiz?

508
00:23:15,830 --> 00:23:17,030
About two months ago.

509
00:23:17,310 --> 00:23:18,390
So you're saying

510
00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:22,270
the pigeon flew for a month and a half?

511
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:23,400
Yes.

512
00:23:23,590 --> 00:23:25,450
The journey from Yenisei Kirghiz

513
00:23:25,830 --> 00:23:27,270
to Chang'an is very long.

514
00:23:28,720 --> 00:23:31,400
It's 6,000 li from Chang'an
to Yenisei Kirghiz.

515
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:33,720
That's certainly far for humans.

516
00:23:33,720 --> 00:23:35,200
But for a carrier pigeon,

517
00:23:35,310 --> 00:23:36,310
it's not that bad.

518
00:23:36,920 --> 00:23:37,720
The mentor, Master Di,

519
00:23:37,720 --> 00:23:39,780
noted in his investigation journals

520
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:41,930
that he once kept a carrier pigeon.

521
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:43,530
It could cover a thousand li

522
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:45,780
and return to its nest in just 4 hours.

523
00:23:45,830 --> 00:23:47,230
Even the slowest pigeons

524
00:23:47,750 --> 00:23:49,280
can easily fly 500 or 600 li

525
00:23:49,350 --> 00:23:50,350
in a single day.

526
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:52,390
Yet your pigeon took

527
00:23:52,720 --> 00:23:55,030
a month and a half to fly 6,000 li.

528
00:23:55,510 --> 00:23:56,400
Sun Zi,

529
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:59,000
despite your serious injuries,

530
00:23:59,310 --> 00:24:00,640
I still need to ask you:

531
00:24:01,110 --> 00:24:01,680
Are you

532
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:03,430
really telling the truth?

533
00:24:03,590 --> 00:24:04,720
How dare you, Sun Zi!

534
00:24:04,830 --> 00:24:05,830
Don't you know that

535
00:24:05,830 --> 00:24:06,960
lying to a constable

536
00:24:07,070 --> 00:24:08,160
is a punishable offense?

537
00:24:08,160 --> 00:24:08,760
All right.

538
00:24:11,110 --> 00:24:13,520
Since you're unwilling to break the rules,

539
00:24:13,590 --> 00:24:16,390
I'll investigate
the source of this intel myself.

540
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:18,880
Wait.

541
00:24:20,350 --> 00:24:21,680
Rules are minor matters

542
00:24:22,550 --> 00:24:24,550
compared to the safety of Chang'an.

543
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:28,070
This intel

544
00:24:28,750 --> 00:24:30,150
was sold to me by someone.

545
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:37,240
I am the owner of the Intel Stall.

546
00:24:38,030 --> 00:24:39,430
I take all kinds of intel,

547
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:40,850
but only if

548
00:24:41,270 --> 00:24:42,310
it's worth the coin.

549
00:24:42,310 --> 00:24:45,200
Is an intel about the capital's safety

550
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:46,480
valuable?

551
00:24:47,790 --> 00:24:48,640
I meet a handful

552
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:50,350
of people like you every day.

553
00:24:50,350 --> 00:24:51,210
Some even claim

554
00:24:51,220 --> 00:24:53,950
it concerns the safety
of the entire Tang Empire.

555
00:24:54,350 --> 00:24:56,830
Soon, Yenisei Kirghiz spies will

556
00:24:56,830 --> 00:24:58,060
enter Chang'an

557
00:24:58,310 --> 00:24:59,270
and meet with their accomplices

558
00:24:59,270 --> 00:25:00,990
hiding here

559
00:25:01,110 --> 00:25:02,640
to plot something big.

560
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:04,160
Does this concern

561
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:06,110
the safety of the capital?

562
00:25:06,180 --> 00:25:08,470
Normally, it wouldn't.

563
00:25:09,440 --> 00:25:10,390
But now...

564
00:25:10,480 --> 00:25:12,480
the international polo tournament

565
00:25:12,510 --> 00:25:13,400
will be played by

566
00:25:13,400 --> 00:25:15,350
the Tang Empire and Yenisei Kirghiz.

567
00:25:15,350 --> 00:25:16,610
The key question is...

568
00:25:21,700 --> 00:25:23,090
Why should I trust you?

569
00:25:24,070 --> 00:25:25,170
You want to know

570
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:27,270
how I got this intel?

571
00:25:27,550 --> 00:25:29,240
I won't reveal anything.

572
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:31,140
That's the rule, isn't it?

573
00:25:31,440 --> 00:25:32,300
So,

574
00:25:32,430 --> 00:25:35,170
it's up to you to take the risk.

575
00:25:35,750 --> 00:25:36,880
How much do you want?

576
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:40,310
30,000 coins,

577
00:25:41,070 --> 00:25:43,270
and I'll tell you the meeting location.

578
00:25:43,640 --> 00:25:44,870
As for the time,

579
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:46,320
it's 3 days from now.

580
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:47,790
At that time,

581
00:25:48,110 --> 00:25:49,870
you just need to wait patiently

582
00:25:50,110 --> 00:25:51,750
for your catch.

583
00:25:51,750 --> 00:25:53,720
Did he tell you the meeting location?

584
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:54,310
Yes.

585
00:25:55,750 --> 00:25:57,550
I wanted to sell the intel first.

586
00:25:57,640 --> 00:25:59,240
Someone would naturally find me.

587
00:25:59,240 --> 00:25:59,780
This way,

588
00:25:59,870 --> 00:26:01,640
I can sell the intel twice,

589
00:26:01,830 --> 00:26:04,720
then sell the meeting location
for another 30,000 coins.

590
00:26:04,720 --> 00:26:06,350
You bought it for 30,000 coins

591
00:26:06,350 --> 00:26:08,070
and planned to sell it for 130,000?

592
00:26:08,070 --> 00:26:09,920
How did you get 130,000 coins?

593
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:13,110
I sold the intel to Liu Xi

594
00:26:13,480 --> 00:26:14,690
for only 10,000 coins.

595
00:26:14,690 --> 00:26:15,600
Liu Xi

596
00:26:15,960 --> 00:26:17,240
bought the intel for 10,000

597
00:26:17,240 --> 00:26:18,510
and sold it for 100,000?

598
00:26:18,510 --> 00:26:19,600
He deserved to die.

599
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:24,090
Are you sure that person had 6 fingers?

600
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:25,030
Yes.

601
00:26:26,740 --> 00:26:27,680
He had 6 fingers

602
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,510
on his right hand.

603
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:36,590
Search the entire city for a man

604
00:26:36,590 --> 00:26:38,390
with 6 fingers on his right hand.

605
00:26:38,790 --> 00:26:40,660
He has a booming voice,

606
00:26:40,920 --> 00:26:41,910
a strong build,

607
00:26:42,070 --> 00:26:43,640
and is over 6 feet tall.

608
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:44,790
Yes.

609
00:26:45,510 --> 00:26:46,980
Don't alert him.

610
00:26:51,110 --> 00:26:53,240
Give me the remaining 3 silver ingots!

611
00:26:53,550 --> 00:26:56,450
One life for 4 silver ingots.

612
00:26:56,720 --> 00:26:58,830
That's not a low price in Chang'an.

613
00:26:58,920 --> 00:27:00,110
I even personally

614
00:27:00,110 --> 00:27:01,770
lured him to the Ghost Market.

615
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:06,260
But you failed.

616
00:27:07,880 --> 00:27:09,780
How dare you come see me?

617
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:11,270
But you never told us

618
00:27:11,310 --> 00:27:12,910
who we were supposed to kill.

619
00:27:13,030 --> 00:27:14,660
Though I escaped,

620
00:27:15,310 --> 00:27:17,280
I still faintly heard...

621
00:27:17,600 --> 00:27:19,400
Yongzhou Judicial Official investigating.

622
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:21,040
Confess who's behind this.

623
00:27:22,590 --> 00:27:24,850
The current Yongzhou Judicial Official

624
00:27:25,030 --> 00:27:26,310
is Lu Lingfeng.

625
00:27:26,790 --> 00:27:28,070
He was once a top-tier

626
00:27:28,110 --> 00:27:29,370
Imperial Guard.

627
00:27:29,590 --> 00:27:31,270
If you'd told us it was him,

628
00:27:31,310 --> 00:27:32,200
my brothers and I

629
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:33,960
would never have gotten involved.

630
00:27:33,960 --> 00:27:35,420
Give me the 3 silver ingots

631
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:38,280
to give my 2 brothers a proper burial.

632
00:27:38,280 --> 00:27:39,400
If you don't,

633
00:27:40,350 --> 00:27:42,380
don't blame me for taking your life.

634
00:27:43,070 --> 00:27:43,550
Okay.

635
00:27:45,130 --> 00:27:46,200
I'll get it for you.

636
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:23,140
If the woman you saw

637
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:24,510
was actually a man in disguise,

638
00:28:24,510 --> 00:28:25,850
then his real face

639
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:27,220
should look like this.

640
00:28:27,750 --> 00:28:29,590
Miss Xijun, that's incredible!

641
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:31,350
I'll immediately have people
from Yongzhou Prefecture

642
00:28:31,350 --> 00:28:32,470
make copies of this portrait

643
00:28:32,470 --> 00:28:33,640
and search for him throughout the city.

644
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,160
Someone who can
disguise himself as a woman

645
00:28:35,160 --> 00:28:36,760
must be skilled with makeup.

646
00:28:37,030 --> 00:28:38,960
Xijun can draw out his appearance,

647
00:28:38,960 --> 00:28:39,790
but we don't know

648
00:28:39,790 --> 00:28:41,920
what disguise he might be wearing now.

649
00:28:42,070 --> 00:28:42,800
Therefore,

650
00:28:43,110 --> 00:28:44,680
the chance of catching him
in the entire city

651
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:45,540
is quite small.

652
00:28:45,880 --> 00:28:47,140
What should we do then?

653
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:52,200
We saw him

654
00:28:52,240 --> 00:28:53,370
in Fengyi District.

655
00:28:55,920 --> 00:28:57,230
Have Jia, Luo, and Liu

656
00:28:57,440 --> 00:28:58,720
each take a copy of the portrait

657
00:28:58,720 --> 00:29:00,070
and search the districts

658
00:29:00,070 --> 00:29:01,270
surrounding Fengyi District

659
00:29:01,270 --> 00:29:02,000
one by one.

660
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:02,690
Yes, sir.

661
00:29:09,550 --> 00:29:10,280
Official Lu.

662
00:29:10,920 --> 00:29:11,580
Please sit.

663
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:15,750
Xijun.

664
00:29:16,590 --> 00:29:17,270
Li Zhuang was my good friend

665
00:29:17,270 --> 00:29:19,160
when I served in the Imperial Guard.

666
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:20,640
Please make some more sushan

667
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:21,440
for him to try.

668
00:29:21,680 --> 00:29:22,210
Alright.

669
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:29,550
Delicious.

670
00:29:32,550 --> 00:29:33,240
General.

671
00:29:33,590 --> 00:29:34,670
You called me here

672
00:29:34,960 --> 00:29:36,640
not just to eat sushan, right?

673
00:29:38,590 --> 00:29:40,650
Not many of our old comrades are left.

674
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:42,840
I truly cherish

675
00:29:43,070 --> 00:29:44,330
this reunion with you.

676
00:29:46,110 --> 00:29:46,960
Indeed.

677
00:29:47,480 --> 00:29:49,070
I've heard about what happened

678
00:29:49,070 --> 00:29:50,200
to Wu and Guo Zhuang.

679
00:30:00,550 --> 00:30:01,880
I'm partly responsible

680
00:30:02,350 --> 00:30:03,440
for their deaths.

681
00:30:04,470 --> 00:30:05,730
I feel ashamed.

682
00:30:07,240 --> 00:30:10,470
Whenever I think about it, my heart hurts.

683
00:30:13,350 --> 00:30:13,960
But...

684
00:30:14,920 --> 00:30:16,300
Wu and Guo Zhuang

685
00:30:16,360 --> 00:30:17,750
lived up
to the Imperial Guard's reputation

686
00:30:17,750 --> 00:30:19,950
of eliminating evil with their swords.

687
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:21,400
They died with honor.

688
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:24,540
What about you?

689
00:30:27,070 --> 00:30:28,530
What do you mean, General?

690
00:30:28,750 --> 00:30:30,240
Now that you work for
the Court of State Ceremonials

691
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,510
and I'm with the Yongzhou Prefecture,

692
00:30:31,510 --> 00:30:33,160
we can drop our old titles.

693
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:33,880
So,

694
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:36,200
are you interrogating me, Official Lu?

695
00:30:36,200 --> 00:30:37,720
If I were interrogating you,

696
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:39,120
would we be sitting here?

697
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:42,640
Back then,

698
00:30:43,480 --> 00:30:45,810
on your first day in the Imperial Guard...

699
00:30:46,070 --> 00:30:46,830
Li Zhuang?

700
00:30:48,400 --> 00:30:50,860
You share the same "Zhuang"
with Guo Zhuang.

701
00:30:50,880 --> 00:30:52,710
What does "Zhuang" mean to you?

702
00:30:53,550 --> 00:30:56,270
Confucius said, "When approached with
dignity, people respond with respect."

703
00:30:56,270 --> 00:30:57,480
As a member of the Imperial Guard,

704
00:30:57,480 --> 00:30:59,240
I'm always at His Majesty's side.

705
00:30:59,240 --> 00:31:00,110
"Zhuang" means that

706
00:31:00,110 --> 00:31:01,400
my every word and action
represent the dignity

707
00:31:01,400 --> 00:31:03,240
and solemnity of the Tang Empire.

708
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:04,100
Well answered.

709
00:31:04,440 --> 00:31:06,680
You'll surely
achieve great things someday.

710
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:08,480
If not for your recommendation,

711
00:31:08,730 --> 00:31:09,750
I might still be

712
00:31:09,750 --> 00:31:11,680
an ordinary Imperial Guard today.

713
00:31:12,310 --> 00:31:13,080
But I believe

714
00:31:13,550 --> 00:31:14,850
you're not bringing this up today

715
00:31:14,850 --> 00:31:16,160
just to reminisce.

716
00:31:16,790 --> 00:31:18,450
If you suspect me, just say so.

717
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:20,000
Fine.

718
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:22,310
I'll be direct then.

719
00:31:25,090 --> 00:31:26,750
After you introduced me to Liu Xi,

720
00:31:26,750 --> 00:31:28,610
I followed him to the Ghost Market

721
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:31,250
and was ambushed at the Intel Stall there.

722
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:33,180
Three assassins with crossbows

723
00:31:33,180 --> 00:31:35,070
tried to kill me.

724
00:31:35,750 --> 00:31:36,640
Apart from you,

725
00:31:37,110 --> 00:31:38,790
no one should have known that

726
00:31:39,110 --> 00:31:41,070
I was investigating
the source of the intel.

727
00:31:41,070 --> 00:31:42,070
And Liu Xi

728
00:31:42,750 --> 00:31:43,590
clearly knew

729
00:31:43,640 --> 00:31:45,900
there were assassins waiting in ambush.

730
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:46,960
Are you all right?

731
00:31:48,070 --> 00:31:50,120
It's certainly possible that

732
00:31:50,270 --> 00:31:52,180
Liu Xi hired those assassins.

733
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:54,080
Because he bought that intel

734
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:55,730
for 10,000 coins,

735
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:01,750
but sold it to you for 100,000 coins.

736
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:06,550
Now that Liu Xi is dead,

737
00:32:06,880 --> 00:32:07,880
there's no way to find out

738
00:32:07,880 --> 00:32:08,920
if the 90,000 coins

739
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:10,780
went completely into his pockets

740
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:13,570
or were split evenly between you two.

741
00:32:13,570 --> 00:32:15,700
Since he was making money through you,

742
00:32:15,750 --> 00:32:18,240
you might even have gotten a bigger share.

743
00:32:21,170 --> 00:32:23,910
Yes, Liu Xi was my informant.

744
00:32:24,350 --> 00:32:25,030
For 2 years,

745
00:32:25,060 --> 00:32:26,840
he provided intel only to me.

746
00:32:27,480 --> 00:32:28,540
Now that he's dead,

747
00:32:28,680 --> 00:32:30,210
I truly can't prove myself.

748
00:32:32,660 --> 00:32:33,400
Li Zhuang!

749
00:32:34,120 --> 00:32:35,620
What are you doing?

750
00:32:36,790 --> 00:32:39,160
My innocence is worth more than my life.

751
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:40,960
Official Lu.

752
00:32:42,190 --> 00:32:43,200
If there is another life,

753
00:32:43,200 --> 00:32:44,200
I would rather spend it

754
00:32:44,200 --> 00:32:46,200
as just an ordinary Imperial Guard,

755
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:48,900
holding my sword firmly

756
00:32:49,440 --> 00:32:51,400
to protect the peace of the capital!

757
00:32:51,400 --> 00:32:52,100
Brother!

758
00:32:58,200 --> 00:32:59,330
Put down your sword.

759
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:00,740
Without dying,

760
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:03,250
I cannot prove my innocence.

761
00:33:03,480 --> 00:33:04,400
I was rash

762
00:33:04,920 --> 00:33:06,780
and made unfounded assumptions.

763
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:09,810
Please forgive me.

764
00:33:26,350 --> 00:33:28,030
I don't deserve to be called "brother"

765
00:33:28,030 --> 00:33:28,960
by you, General.

766
00:33:29,200 --> 00:33:31,000
Despite your years of mentorship,

767
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:32,690
I failed to achieve anything.

768
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:35,160
I was desperate too.

769
00:33:36,590 --> 00:33:38,680
I didn't pocket a single coin
from the 100,000 coins.

770
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:40,240
If you don't believe me,
search my quarters.

771
00:33:40,240 --> 00:33:41,040
I believe you.

772
00:33:43,160 --> 00:33:45,110
It's all right now.

773
00:33:45,240 --> 00:33:46,480
To everyone present,

774
00:33:46,510 --> 00:33:48,000
all the sushan before you

775
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,800
are now completely free.

776
00:33:49,830 --> 00:33:51,640
It's on me, Boss Fei!

777
00:33:51,720 --> 00:33:53,160
It's fine, it's fine.

778
00:33:54,850 --> 00:33:56,180
That scared me to death.

779
00:33:56,350 --> 00:33:56,960
Sit.

780
00:34:00,070 --> 00:34:00,670
Li Zhuang.

781
00:34:01,310 --> 00:34:02,910
You need to carefully recall

782
00:34:03,270 --> 00:34:04,750
who else knew

783
00:34:05,070 --> 00:34:07,130
about my investigation of this lead.

784
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:10,400
After we parted,

785
00:34:10,590 --> 00:34:12,230
I went to the Yongzhou Prefecture.

786
00:34:12,230 --> 00:34:13,400
The Yongzhou Prefecture?

787
00:34:13,400 --> 00:34:13,920
Yes.

788
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:15,320
The Polo Tournament this time

789
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:16,400
is co-hosted by
the Court of State Ceremonials

790
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:17,920
and the Yongzhou Prefecture.

791
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:19,250
So we need to meet daily.

792
00:34:19,590 --> 00:34:21,230
The Tournament is approaching.

793
00:34:21,230 --> 00:34:23,230
I have so many things to take care of.

794
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:25,280
These so-called daily meetings

795
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:26,870
are just a formality.

796
00:34:27,230 --> 00:34:28,090
How about this?

797
00:34:28,590 --> 00:34:30,480
From now on, Li Zhuang will be the liaison

798
00:34:30,480 --> 00:34:32,480
for the Court of State Ceremonials.

799
00:34:33,030 --> 00:34:33,670
Li Zhuang,

800
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:35,650
if there's nothing important,

801
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:37,460
you don't need to report to me.

802
00:34:38,280 --> 00:34:38,800
Yes.

803
00:34:39,920 --> 00:34:42,110
As for Yongzhou Prefecture,

804
00:34:42,139 --> 00:34:43,960
Magistrate Liu will be in charge.

805
00:34:43,960 --> 00:34:44,969
Liu Jun,

806
00:34:45,150 --> 00:34:46,469
we are just assisting.

807
00:34:46,550 --> 00:34:49,110
Follow
the Court of State Ceremonials' lead.

808
00:34:50,150 --> 00:34:50,710
Yes.

809
00:34:54,630 --> 00:34:55,190
Li.

810
00:34:55,230 --> 00:34:56,159
Magistrate Liu.

811
00:34:56,280 --> 00:34:58,110
Since Magistrate Liu is a liaison,

812
00:34:58,110 --> 00:34:58,710
I thought

813
00:34:58,760 --> 00:35:00,670
he should know about
the Yenisei Kirghiz spies

814
00:35:00,670 --> 00:35:02,070
infiltrating Chang'an.

815
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:03,000
Besides,

816
00:35:03,150 --> 00:35:04,320
didn't His Majesty assign

817
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:05,840
the case to the Yongzhou Prefecture?

818
00:35:05,840 --> 00:35:06,440
Liu Jun?

819
00:35:07,110 --> 00:35:08,510
No one else knows about this?

820
00:35:08,510 --> 00:35:09,070
No one.

821
00:35:16,670 --> 00:35:17,230
Xijun,

822
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:18,480
please do me a favor.

823
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:19,280
Go to Su Wuming

824
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,590
and ask him for Yingtao.

825
00:35:20,590 --> 00:35:22,510
But Wuming just became the county sheriff,

826
00:35:22,510 --> 00:35:24,570
and he's very busy in Wannian County.

827
00:35:25,550 --> 00:35:26,960
What should we do now?

828
00:35:27,700 --> 00:35:29,280
What's troubling you?

829
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:32,620
I need someone reliable to follow

830
00:35:33,690 --> 00:35:35,750
Liu Jun, the Magistrate of Yongzhou.

831
00:35:35,880 --> 00:35:36,840
But I just sent

832
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:38,150
Jia and the others out.

833
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:39,230
Liu Jun?

834
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:41,480
Liu Jun is just a scholar.

835
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:44,300
He's not very suspicious.

836
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:46,370
But we still need to investigate.

837
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:50,480
Then let me try.

838
00:35:50,710 --> 00:35:51,360
You?

839
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:53,510
We've traveled south and west together.

840
00:35:53,510 --> 00:35:55,110
I've witnessed the way you and Wuming

841
00:35:55,110 --> 00:35:56,480
solve those mysterious cases

842
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:57,110
and learned

843
00:35:57,110 --> 00:35:58,320
a thing or two.

844
00:35:59,030 --> 00:36:01,090
Please give me a chance, Official Lu.

845
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:04,030
A scholar.

846
00:36:06,550 --> 00:36:07,150
Very well.

847
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,070
Just follow him from a distance

848
00:36:09,070 --> 00:36:10,520
and note where he goes.

849
00:36:10,650 --> 00:36:12,070
You must be extremely careful

850
00:36:12,070 --> 00:36:13,870
and return to Sushan Shop

851
00:36:14,030 --> 00:36:14,920
before 7 pm.

852
00:36:16,230 --> 00:36:17,760
[Yongzhou Prefecture]

853
00:36:50,790 --> 00:36:53,880
[Dayu Fish Market]

854
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:55,480
The fish today is huge.

855
00:36:55,480 --> 00:36:56,550
We can prepare it in two ways.

856
00:36:56,550 --> 00:36:58,280
The middle part can be eaten raw.

857
00:36:58,280 --> 00:36:59,320
The head can be used for soup.

858
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:00,110
It's so fresh,

859
00:37:00,110 --> 00:37:02,510
it'll taste good
no matter how it's cooked.

860
00:37:04,590 --> 00:37:05,440
